high_descs: Walk to the left side of the table straight ahead.
Grab the lettuce between the cup and tomato on the counter.
Turn left, walk to the fridge to your right, when you reach the fridge turn left to face the sink.
Place the lettuce in the sink, wash it and remove it.
Turn left, walk to the stove, when you reach the stove, turn left, walk straight and then make a quick right to the waste basket to the side of the stove.
Place the lettuce inside the waste basket.
anns.task_desc: Place clean lettuce inside the waste basket.

high_descs: Walk over to the left side of the table in front of you.
Pick up the closest head of lettuce off of the table.
Turn left and walk over to the sink.
Wash the head of lettuce in the sink then pick it back up.
Turn left and walk over to the counter, then turn left and walk forward, turn right and walk up to the green bin that is next to the oven.
Put the clean head of lettuce in the green bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean head of lettuce in a green bin.

high_descs: Turn to the left and walk to the end of the island.
Pick up the lettuce that is between the glass and the tomato on the island.
Turn to the left and walk to the sink.
Place the lettuce in the sink, turn the water on, rinse the lettuce, turn the water off, and remove the lettuce.
Turn to the left and walk past the stove to the garbage bin that is to the left of the stove.
Place the lettuce into the garbage bin.
